1
00:00:35,966 --> 00:00:38,566
=Angels and Guards=

2
00:00:38,600 --> 00:00:41,133
=Episode 23=

3
00:00:41,333 --> 00:00:42,933
- What happened?
- I don't know.

4
00:00:42,933 --> 00:00:44,666
How would I know?

5
00:00:47,366 --> 00:00:48,133
What are you doing?

6
00:00:48,166 --> 00:00:49,933
This is the Jinyiwei Northern Bureau,

7
00:00:50,766 --> 00:00:51,933
not a marketplace.

8
00:00:53,533 --> 00:00:55,566
My lord, I'm carrying out my orders

9
00:00:55,833 --> 00:00:57,866
and checking for suspicious people
among the Jinyiwei.

10
00:00:58,266 --> 00:01:00,133
What kind of stupid order is that?

11
00:01:00,400 --> 00:01:02,600
Which fool gave you

12
00:01:02,600 --> 00:01:03,766
such a stupid order?

13
00:01:04,666 --> 00:01:05,166
My lord.

14
00:01:05,600 --> 00:01:08,266
I'm the fool who gave
that stupid order.

15
00:01:08,933 --> 00:01:10,266
Feng Fuliu is skilled in disguise.

16
00:01:10,566 --> 00:01:12,566
I only wanted to be safe.

17
00:01:16,866 --> 00:01:18,366
You people do nothing useful.

18
00:01:23,000 --> 00:01:23,600
Are you mad?

19
00:01:24,033 --> 00:01:25,600
I was afraid Feng Fuliu

20
00:01:25,766 --> 00:01:27,800
might disguise himself
as the Commander.

21
00:01:29,700 --> 00:01:31,433
Is it swollen or not?

22
00:01:31,433 --> 00:01:33,200
It's swollen! Very swollen!

23
00:01:34,500 --> 00:01:35,266
It was Mr. Lu.

24
00:01:35,566 --> 00:01:36,733
He ordered it.

25
00:01:36,833 --> 00:01:39,700
He said to pinch everyone hard.

26
00:01:39,833 --> 00:01:40,766
Yes, it was Mr. Lu.

27
00:01:40,766 --> 00:01:41,533
What are you doing?

28
00:01:41,566 --> 00:01:42,400
What nonsense are you saying?

29
00:01:43,266 --> 00:01:44,333
What are you talking about?

30
00:01:45,066 --> 00:01:45,566
I...

31
00:01:45,566 --> 00:01:47,166
Wasn't that what you ordered?

32
00:01:50,166 --> 00:01:51,700
You two obey to my face

33
00:01:51,766 --> 00:01:53,433
and betray me behind my back.

34
00:01:56,266 --> 00:01:57,666
We are so wronged!

35
00:01:58,200 --> 00:02:00,533
We have been on duty here since dawn,

36
00:02:00,733 --> 00:02:01,166
yet

37
00:02:01,666 --> 00:02:04,533
you accuse us of betraying you
behind your back.

38
00:02:06,200 --> 00:02:06,733
Exactly.

39
00:02:07,000 --> 00:02:08,233
Enough, enough.

40
00:02:08,766 --> 00:02:09,600
You too.

41
00:02:13,166 --> 00:02:13,733
Move.

42
00:02:18,700 --> 00:02:19,600
Come with me.

43
00:02:26,533 --> 00:02:28,133
- My turn! Hua.
- Hua!

44
00:02:29,333 --> 00:02:31,533
How long are you going
to keep sulking?

45
00:02:32,700 --> 00:02:33,800
Do you really think

46
00:02:33,933 --> 00:02:35,866
the court has wronged you?

47
00:02:37,533 --> 00:02:38,533
Let me tell you.

48
00:02:40,200 --> 00:02:41,700
Once you join the Jinyiwei,

49
00:02:42,333 --> 00:02:43,900
your life is no longer your own.

50
00:02:48,266 --> 00:02:48,866
Bingfan.

51
00:02:49,666 --> 00:02:50,666
Did your father

52
00:02:51,533 --> 00:02:52,766
never tell you?

53
00:02:54,033 --> 00:02:55,733
In the world of the Jinyiwei,

54
00:02:56,266 --> 00:02:57,333
there is only execution,

55
00:02:57,700 --> 00:02:58,600
not questions.

56
00:02:59,100 --> 00:03:00,166
There is only obedience,

57
00:03:00,666 --> 00:03:01,566
not grievance.

58
00:03:02,033 --> 00:03:03,233
And now you even dare

59
00:03:03,866 --> 00:03:05,300
to defy your superiors.

60
00:03:06,766 --> 00:03:08,766
We were carrying
out our assigned task.

61
00:03:09,033 --> 00:03:09,733
Excuses!

62
00:03:10,533 --> 00:03:11,533
The three of you

63
00:03:12,066 --> 00:03:14,733
want to make a joke
of my Northern Bureau.

64
00:03:15,733 --> 00:03:17,466
You are Jinyiwei too.

65
00:03:18,233 --> 00:03:20,300
If Feng Fuliu succeeds,

66
00:03:21,100 --> 00:03:22,600
the Northern Bureau

67
00:03:23,066 --> 00:03:24,433
will become a laughingstock.

68
00:03:25,533 --> 00:03:26,533
Feng Fuliu

69
00:03:26,933 --> 00:03:27,633
is a top fugitive

70
00:03:27,666 --> 00:03:30,733
on the Bounty List,
second only to Leng Xin.

71
00:03:32,533 --> 00:03:34,433
Will you let him go

72
00:03:34,600 --> 00:03:36,033
just because your feelings were hurt?

73
00:03:39,666 --> 00:03:41,400
You don't deserve to be Jinyiwei.

74
00:03:43,900 --> 00:03:44,000
I...

75
00:03:44,033 --> 00:03:44,533
Get out!

76
00:03:53,400 --> 00:03:54,500
You have

77
00:03:56,500 --> 00:03:57,333
disappointed me deeply.

78
00:04:00,800 --> 00:04:07,700
(Northern Bureau)

79
00:05:01,500 --> 00:05:02,400
What are you doing?

80
00:05:02,600 --> 00:05:03,800
I heard the three of you

81
00:05:03,833 --> 00:05:04,933
have been slacking off
at the Northern Bureau.

82
00:05:06,733 --> 00:05:08,766
No, we...

83
00:05:09,333 --> 00:05:10,000
You what?

84
00:05:11,833 --> 00:05:12,366
We are disappointed.

85
00:05:12,766 --> 00:05:14,100
We no longer want to serve the court.

86
00:05:17,533 --> 00:05:18,033
Fine.

87
00:05:19,666 --> 00:05:21,033
Then take off your Flying Fish Robe,

88
00:05:21,100 --> 00:05:22,033
hand over your Embroidered Spring Blade,

89
00:05:22,666 --> 00:05:23,266
and get out.

90
00:05:24,166 --> 00:05:25,100
Why are you saying that?

91
00:05:25,600 --> 00:05:26,933
Because I'm disappointed in you.

92
00:05:27,166 --> 00:05:29,566
The Shen Bingfan I knew feared nothing.

93
00:05:29,700 --> 00:05:30,633
Every setback only made her stronger.

94
00:05:30,666 --> 00:05:32,000
Qiankun Rat,

95
00:05:32,400 --> 00:05:33,400
Diaotu, the Flower-Picking Bee...

96
00:05:33,600 --> 00:05:34,366
None of them scared her.

97
00:05:34,833 --> 00:05:36,833
Now, one little grievance breaks you?

98
00:05:39,400 --> 00:05:41,933
Do you still remember
why you joined the Jinyiwei?

99
00:05:42,600 --> 00:05:44,166
Why did you come to the Northern Bureau?

100
00:05:44,700 --> 00:05:45,366
Your blood feud

101
00:05:45,666 --> 00:05:47,433
and the mission you carry.
Have you forgotten?

102
00:05:48,033 --> 00:05:48,700
I haven't.

103
00:05:52,200 --> 00:05:53,566
It just hurts.

104
00:05:54,900 --> 00:05:56,100
People die every day.

105
00:05:56,566 --> 00:05:57,900
Today, it may be someone else.

106
00:05:58,566 --> 00:06:00,600
Tomorrow, it may be your family
or friends.

107
00:06:01,533 --> 00:06:02,266
So what?

108
00:06:03,766 --> 00:06:05,033
The sun still rises.

109
00:06:06,033 --> 00:06:06,400
Darkness

110
00:06:07,033 --> 00:06:08,566
will always break before dawn.

111
00:06:11,433 --> 00:06:12,100
And Leng Xin.

112
00:06:14,566 --> 00:06:15,466
Will you stop hunting him?

113
00:06:21,166 --> 00:06:22,266
You said all this

114
00:06:23,666 --> 00:06:25,566
because you want me
to catch Feng Fuliu?

115
00:06:25,666 --> 00:06:26,500
Yes.

116
00:06:27,533 --> 00:06:29,300
But if I catch Feng Fuliu,
what about you?

117
00:06:38,933 --> 00:06:39,600
What about me?

118
00:06:42,533 --> 00:06:43,800
I want you to catch Feng Fuliu.

119
00:06:44,733 --> 00:06:45,833
I want you to be safe.

120
00:06:49,433 --> 00:06:50,100
As for me,

121
00:06:52,033 --> 00:06:53,066
you don't need to worry.

122
00:06:55,700 --> 00:06:57,633
Before I fulfill my promise to you,

123
00:07:00,200 --> 00:07:01,400
nothing will happen to me.

124
00:07:19,400 --> 00:07:21,000
Hua, where are we going later?

125
00:07:22,400 --> 00:07:23,166
How about hot pot,

126
00:07:23,200 --> 00:07:23,733
Bingfan?

127
00:07:25,000 --> 00:07:25,566
I have decided.

128
00:07:26,433 --> 00:07:27,533
I will catch the phantom thief
Feng Fuliu.

129
00:07:28,666 --> 00:07:29,700
I need your help.

130
00:07:31,433 --> 00:07:33,033
Whoever Bingfan says we catch,
we catch.

131
00:07:35,666 --> 00:07:36,266
Duoyu.

132
00:07:37,033 --> 00:07:37,966
I need you to make me

133
00:07:38,000 --> 00:07:39,566
a perfect plan.

134
00:07:41,733 --> 00:07:42,300
Bingfan.

135
00:07:43,166 --> 00:07:43,700
But

136
00:07:44,266 --> 00:07:46,500
the sun sets in two hours.

137
00:07:47,600 --> 00:07:50,133
You want me to make a plan now?

138
00:07:50,333 --> 00:07:51,500
That is why we must hurry.

139
00:07:52,066 --> 00:07:52,500
This time,

140
00:07:53,266 --> 00:07:54,533
we can't let him escape again.

141
00:08:12,133 --> 00:08:14,866
(The Phantom Thief Feng Fuliu)

142
00:08:25,066 --> 00:08:25,466
Hurry.

143
00:08:33,566 --> 00:08:34,300
Mr. Lu's order.

144
00:08:35,233 --> 00:08:37,000
The password changes every hour.

145
00:08:37,200 --> 00:08:37,533
Yes.

146
00:08:46,433 --> 00:08:47,033
Hua.

147
00:08:47,533 --> 00:08:48,233
Late-night snack.

148
00:08:49,900 --> 00:08:50,800
Good boy.

149
00:08:51,533 --> 00:08:52,933
Feed me.

150
00:08:53,200 --> 00:08:53,900
All right.

151
00:08:58,433 --> 00:08:59,000
Here.

152
00:09:05,266 --> 00:09:06,166
Your hands...

153
00:09:06,866 --> 00:09:08,533
Did you wash them?

154
00:09:09,766 --> 00:09:12,466
Don't worry. I washed them
many times.

155
00:09:13,000 --> 00:09:14,566
Hua, you are so beautiful.

156
00:09:15,166 --> 00:09:16,100
Let me replace you for a while.

157
00:09:19,166 --> 00:09:19,600
Who are you?

158
00:09:20,400 --> 00:09:22,000
Duoyu would never talk like that.

159
00:09:22,266 --> 00:09:24,366
Hua, what are you joking about?

160
00:09:30,566 --> 00:09:32,066
Guards! Catch the thief!

161
00:09:32,833 --> 00:09:34,033
Feng Fuliu is disguised as Xu Duoyu!

162
00:09:34,733 --> 00:09:35,133
After him!

163
00:09:35,400 --> 00:09:35,900
Yes.

164
00:09:35,900 --> 00:09:37,133
Feng Fuliu is disguised as Xu Duoyu!

165
00:09:37,533 --> 00:09:40,133
Catch him! Catch Xu Duoyu!

166
00:09:41,700 --> 00:09:42,600
Catch Xu Duoyu!

167
00:09:42,733 --> 00:09:44,100
Xu Duoyu is Feng Fuliu in disguise!

168
00:09:44,733 --> 00:09:45,633
Who

169
00:09:46,533 --> 00:09:47,066
locked the door from the outside

170
00:09:47,333 --> 00:09:48,233
while I was

171
00:09:48,700 --> 00:09:49,933
in the latrine?

172
00:09:50,766 --> 00:09:52,366
Who was it? Who is that rotten?

173
00:09:54,666 --> 00:09:55,333
Feng Fuliu!

174
00:09:58,366 --> 00:09:58,800
Get him!

175
00:10:01,333 --> 00:10:02,000
Move!

176
00:10:02,933 --> 00:10:04,266
Why are you taking me?

177
00:10:04,833 --> 00:10:05,600
Hua.

178
00:10:06,233 --> 00:10:06,933
Mr. Zhang is here.

179
00:10:11,066 --> 00:10:12,000
Why are you here too?

180
00:10:12,200 --> 00:10:13,366
Your Commander

181
00:10:13,566 --> 00:10:14,600
asked me to come help.

182
00:10:17,666 --> 00:10:19,200
Why are you holding Xu Duoyu down?

183
00:10:19,533 --> 00:10:21,466
I thought he was Feng Fuliu
in disguise.

184
00:10:22,166 --> 00:10:22,866
I'm not!

185
00:10:23,166 --> 00:10:23,533
You...

186
00:10:23,900 --> 00:10:24,666
Hua!

187
00:10:25,433 --> 00:10:26,466
Save me!

188
00:10:27,066 --> 00:10:28,000
You really are not?

189
00:10:29,166 --> 00:10:30,500
I really am not!

190
00:10:34,233 --> 00:10:35,133
It hurts!

191
00:10:35,900 --> 00:10:36,266
My lord,

192
00:10:36,566 --> 00:10:37,466
it seems he is not Feng Fuliu.

193
00:10:37,566 --> 00:10:38,966
You really are the real one?

194
00:10:39,400 --> 00:10:40,600
I was in the latrine just now.

195
00:10:41,233 --> 00:10:42,966
Someone locked the door
from the outside.

196
00:10:43,866 --> 00:10:45,800
I barely managed to break out.

197
00:10:48,900 --> 00:10:49,766
It is all swollen.

198
00:10:49,933 --> 00:10:51,133
You made such a scene

199
00:10:51,366 --> 00:10:52,766
and drew everyone here.

200
00:10:53,166 --> 00:10:54,733
Who is guarding the Twin Dragon Jade?

201
00:10:57,533 --> 00:10:58,100
Oh no.

202
00:10:58,333 --> 00:10:59,000
Go!

203
00:11:01,400 --> 00:11:01,733
Password.

204
00:11:02,100 --> 00:11:02,833
Thieves tremble.

205
00:11:03,033 --> 00:11:03,466
Response.

206
00:11:03,700 --> 00:11:04,300
Jinyiwei strike.

207
00:11:07,533 --> 00:11:07,966
Wait.

208
00:11:09,566 --> 00:11:11,000
We can't all go in.

209
00:11:11,033 --> 00:11:13,266
What if Feng Fuliu is hiding
among us?

210
00:11:14,866 --> 00:11:16,066
The Commander and I will go in.

211
00:11:16,866 --> 00:11:17,366
Hold on.

212
00:11:18,533 --> 00:11:19,433
Young Duke.

213
00:11:20,333 --> 00:11:22,533
Why are you so interested
in the Twin Dragon Jade?

214
00:11:23,900 --> 00:11:24,966
I'm here to help you.

215
00:11:25,900 --> 00:11:27,066
You still suspect me?

216
00:11:28,533 --> 00:11:30,433
Given your relationship
with Princess Pingyang,

217
00:11:31,066 --> 00:11:32,166
when her manor was robbed,

218
00:11:32,733 --> 00:11:34,100
you were never this worried.

219
00:11:34,400 --> 00:11:34,966
So why is it

220
00:11:35,000 --> 00:11:37,000
that when our Commander's
Twin Dragon Jade is in danger,

221
00:11:37,566 --> 00:11:40,266
you, a Young Duke who claims
to avoid politics,

222
00:11:40,366 --> 00:11:41,533
suddenly care so much?

223
00:11:42,533 --> 00:11:43,566
What do you mean?

224
00:11:44,866 --> 00:11:46,733
You are not Chang Beiming.
You are Feng Fuliu.

225
00:11:48,833 --> 00:11:49,100
What?

226
00:11:51,066 --> 00:11:51,666
Chief Squad Leader Hua.

227
00:11:52,233 --> 00:11:53,300
You are clever indeed.

228
00:11:53,733 --> 00:11:54,566
But you're always

229
00:11:55,400 --> 00:11:56,466
one move behind.

230
00:11:57,866 --> 00:11:58,866
Feng Fuliu!

231
00:11:58,866 --> 00:11:59,466
Step back!

232
00:11:59,733 --> 00:12:01,600
Or I'll kill him!

233
00:12:16,366 --> 00:12:16,966
Xu Duoyu.

234
00:12:17,200 --> 00:12:18,066
What's going on?

235
00:12:18,900 --> 00:12:19,800
I don't know.

236
00:12:20,033 --> 00:12:20,733
Right, right.

237
00:12:21,600 --> 00:12:23,833
If Feng Fuliu can impersonate
Xu Duoyu,

238
00:12:24,533 --> 00:12:25,600
he can impersonate the Young Duke,
too.

239
00:12:27,600 --> 00:12:28,000
Get it.

240
00:12:47,533 --> 00:12:48,200
Go on.

241
00:13:01,166 --> 00:13:03,533
It's fine. I have patience.

242
00:13:21,033 --> 00:13:21,866
It's all right.

243
00:13:22,833 --> 00:13:24,000
Step aside and rest.

244
00:13:55,866 --> 00:13:56,533
Shen Bingfan.

245
00:13:57,266 --> 00:13:58,000
You have gotten smarter.

246
00:14:17,100 --> 00:14:18,033
Who are you really?

247
00:14:19,666 --> 00:14:20,700
Who am I?

248
00:14:22,433 --> 00:14:23,933
Come up and see for yourself.

249
00:14:25,033 --> 00:14:26,533
Are you Chang Beiming or not?

250
00:14:27,700 --> 00:14:30,066
If I'm, will you let me go?

251
00:14:31,566 --> 00:14:32,333
Surround him.

252
00:14:32,900 --> 00:14:33,966
He is trying to steal the credit again.

253
00:14:34,400 --> 00:14:34,966
Surround him.

254
00:14:45,166 --> 00:14:45,833
Are you Mr. Zhang

255
00:14:46,200 --> 00:14:46,900
or Shen Bingfan?

256
00:14:48,000 --> 00:14:48,900
Mr. Lu, it is me.

257
00:14:50,333 --> 00:14:51,200
Get him now.

258
00:14:51,700 --> 00:14:52,300
Mr. Lu.

259
00:14:53,500 --> 00:14:54,366
I have surrendered.

260
00:14:55,200 --> 00:14:56,133
Come arrest me yourself.

261
00:15:02,366 --> 00:15:02,900
What?

262
00:15:05,433 --> 00:15:06,000
Arrest me.

263
00:15:15,033 --> 00:15:16,033
That's it?

264
00:15:16,666 --> 00:15:17,600
How come?

265
00:15:18,100 --> 00:15:18,800
You get me.

266
00:15:20,833 --> 00:15:21,600
That means you win.

267
00:15:23,100 --> 00:15:24,033
Why are you still unsatisfied?

268
00:15:24,733 --> 00:15:25,833
It shouldn't be like this.

269
00:15:25,866 --> 00:15:26,366
I...

270
00:15:26,366 --> 00:15:26,700
Shen Bingfan.

271
00:15:27,166 --> 00:15:28,066
Why are you hesitating?

272
00:15:28,200 --> 00:15:29,466
Move. Let me do it.

273
00:15:46,066 --> 00:15:48,500
(Since Feng Fuliu loves disguises
and tricks,)

274
00:15:49,366 --> 00:15:50,766
(why not use his own trick
against him?)

275
00:15:56,000 --> 00:15:57,166
It burns!

276
00:16:04,533 --> 00:16:05,266
It burns!

277
00:16:07,900 --> 00:16:08,500
Gosh!

278
00:16:22,333 --> 00:16:23,333
Why are there two Messrs. Lus?

279
00:16:23,333 --> 00:16:24,000
I see two too.

280
00:16:24,200 --> 00:16:24,700
Yes.

281
00:16:25,400 --> 00:16:26,166
Two Messrs. Lus.

282
00:16:27,100 --> 00:16:27,766
What is going on?

283
00:16:42,766 --> 00:16:44,100
Feng Fuliu disguised himself
as Mr. Lu.

284
00:16:44,566 --> 00:16:45,433
Scum, Feng Fuliu!

285
00:16:45,933 --> 00:16:47,666
How dare you impersonate me?

286
00:16:47,900 --> 00:16:49,766
Nonsense. I'm Lu Guokai!

287
00:16:50,200 --> 00:16:50,800
You are the fake.

288
00:16:51,033 --> 00:16:51,733
Zuo Da. Jiang Biao.

289
00:16:52,233 --> 00:16:52,500
Yes!

290
00:16:52,766 --> 00:16:54,100
Take this fake Lu Guokai.

291
00:16:54,500 --> 00:16:54,833
Yes!

292
00:16:55,433 --> 00:16:56,000
I dare anyone to try!

293
00:17:00,066 --> 00:17:02,166
Bingfan, you were so close.

294
00:17:02,666 --> 00:17:03,600
Which one is real?

295
00:17:04,100 --> 00:17:05,366
Look carefully.

296
00:17:05,400 --> 00:17:05,600
I...

297
00:17:05,600 --> 00:17:06,033
Well...

298
00:17:06,066 --> 00:17:07,833
The smoke was too thick.
I didn't see clearly.

299
00:17:08,033 --> 00:17:08,433
Ask them.

300
00:17:08,666 --> 00:17:09,766
Ask them questions, then.

301
00:17:10,733 --> 00:17:11,100
Yes.

302
00:17:11,333 --> 00:17:11,733
Right.

303
00:17:12,033 --> 00:17:12,400
Exactly.

304
00:17:13,000 --> 00:17:13,566
Mr. Lu.

305
00:17:14,000 --> 00:17:15,100
Do you remember

306
00:17:15,266 --> 00:17:16,800
what you said to me

307
00:17:17,033 --> 00:17:17,733
when you were drunk the other day?

308
00:17:20,066 --> 00:17:22,066
Nonsense. I drank so much that day

309
00:17:22,533 --> 00:17:23,466
and said so many things.

310
00:17:23,733 --> 00:17:24,733
How would I know which one?

311
00:17:24,733 --> 00:17:25,400
The one where

312
00:17:26,000 --> 00:17:28,200
you lamented being born
at the wrong time

313
00:17:28,366 --> 00:17:29,133
and having no chance to rise.

314
00:17:29,666 --> 00:17:30,400
The last line.

315
00:17:31,866 --> 00:17:32,233
The last line.

316
00:17:32,233 --> 00:17:32,933
Wasn't it

317
00:17:34,033 --> 00:17:35,633
If I had the right connections,

318
00:17:36,100 --> 00:17:37,633
I would already be Commander?

319
00:17:38,066 --> 00:17:38,900
He is real!

320
00:17:39,500 --> 00:17:40,200
He is real!

321
00:17:42,500 --> 00:17:43,233
You two fools.

322
00:17:43,533 --> 00:17:45,433
How could you say that here?

323
00:17:45,833 --> 00:17:46,833
- Seize him!
- Yes!

324
00:17:47,000 --> 00:17:47,533
Idiots!

325
00:17:47,700 --> 00:17:48,600
Is my leg crippled?

326
00:17:48,866 --> 00:17:49,566
He is the fake.

327
00:17:49,900 --> 00:17:50,833
After him!

328
00:17:51,666 --> 00:17:52,233
Go!

329
00:17:52,533 --> 00:17:53,466
- After him!
- Move, move!

330
00:17:53,533 --> 00:17:54,400
Catch him! He is the fake!

331
00:17:54,400 --> 00:17:55,100
Out of the way!

332
00:17:55,733 --> 00:17:56,900
- Stop!
- After him!

333
00:18:10,666 --> 00:18:11,666
Feng Fuliu.

334
00:18:12,000 --> 00:18:13,366
Let's see where you run now.

335
00:18:14,000 --> 00:18:14,833
I want to see

336
00:18:15,066 --> 00:18:16,333
who you really are.

337
00:18:19,866 --> 00:18:20,800
Spare me!

338
00:18:21,333 --> 00:18:23,166
Don't kill my wife and children!

339
00:18:23,566 --> 00:18:24,633
Spare me!

340
00:18:26,066 --> 00:18:28,333
Advisor Dong, you are
the phantom thief Feng Fuliu?

341
00:18:44,500 --> 00:18:47,666
♪Because you once entered my dreams♪

342
00:18:48,033 --> 00:18:51,400
♪Truth and illusion blur in wine♪

343
00:18:51,666 --> 00:18:54,666
♪My heart drifted lost♪

344
00:18:54,666 --> 00:18:58,066
♪Yet found you in the crowd♪

345
00:18:59,166 --> 00:19:02,366
♪My blood still burns
as the world surges♪

346
00:19:02,800 --> 00:19:06,133
♪The land is fair, and you are free♪

347
00:19:06,700 --> 00:19:08,900
♪Sword drawn, lost in obsession♪

348
00:19:08,933 --> 00:19:12,966
♪I've softly let it go♪

349
00:19:12,966 --> 00:19:16,833
♪The vow you made was true♪

350
00:19:16,833 --> 00:19:20,566
♪Yet like clouds, it stops for no one♪

351
00:19:20,900 --> 00:19:22,800
♪Put away those dreamlike words♪

352
00:19:22,800 --> 00:19:27,333
♪And forget at world's end♪

353
00:19:27,633 --> 00:19:29,133
♪Embracing memory♪

354
00:19:29,133 --> 00:19:31,500
♪Through blossoms and dreams♪

355
00:19:31,500 --> 00:19:35,366
♪You hide in the crowd, silent♪

356
00:19:35,400 --> 00:19:37,700
♪I wish to let it pass♪

357
00:19:37,700 --> 00:19:42,700
♪And run toward this vast life♪
